item.title: MOTE-NAS: Multi-Objective Training-based Estimate for Efficient Neural Architecture Search
item.description: MOTE-NAS: A new multi-objective training-based estimate drastically improves neural architecture search efficiency, achieving state-of-the-art accuracy with significantly reduced costs.
